headline: Tim NeCastro to retire as president and CEO of Erie Insurance
summary: Erie Insurance (Nasdaq: ERIE) today announced that Tim NeCastro will retire as president and chief executive officer on Dec. 31, 2026, concluding a 30-year career with the company, including 10 years as CEO.
